  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the expression&nbsp;<span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\"></span> , <span class=\"italic\">p</span> is a constant. This expression is equivalent to the expression <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"6 x squared minus 155 x plus 24\"></span></span>. What is the value of <span class=\"italic\">p</span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
